These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, hip-hop, reggae
1. the fan of reggae is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | hip-hop | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different pets are kept: pony, mouse, goat
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Pet   | pony | goat | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, airplane, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Transport   | airplane | trike | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | rock-climbing | gardening |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, rock, d&b
1. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
2. the fan of punk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | rock | d&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, animation, spy
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | animation | spy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, juice
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |       2       |  3  |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | almond-milk | juice |

